🍏 Tim Cook held his final presentation as Apple CEO

At WWDC 2026, Apple put artificial intelligence front and center, unveiling Siri AI — a new assistant powered by Google's Gemini model.

Here's what else was announced:

▪️ Siri AI will be integrated across all iOS apps;
▪️ AI will be able to search files, analyze documents, and edit photos;
▪️ iOS 27 will be available on iPhones starting with the iPhone 11;
▪️ Expanded parental controls are coming to the system;
▪️ The Passwords app will automatically replace compromised passwords;
▪️ The Calendar app will gain menstrual cycle tracking;
▪️ AirPods will get a built-in equalizer.

What do you think — a real breakthrough or is Apple running out of ways to impress? 🤔📱
